# Gateway

### Status page
GET http://localhost:2000/status
Accept: application/json

### Ping all services
GET http://localhost:2000/ping
Accept: application/json

### Ping user services
GET http://localhost:2000/user/ping
Accept: application/json

### Ping auth services
GET http://localhost:2000/auth/ping
Accept: application/json

### All users
GET http://localhost:2000/user
Accept: application/json

### Login
POST http://localhost:2000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=username&password=password

### Register
POST http://localhost:2000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=username&password=password&name=name&email=email@email.com

